force-节点重量与连线牵引力 ​

Vue2 版本 ​

layout-force-options-pro.vue ​

javascript
<template>
  <div>
    <div style="height:calc(100vh);">
      <RelationGraph
        ref="graphRef"
        :options="graphOptions"
        :on-node-click="onNodeClick"
        :on-line-click="onLineClick"
      >
        <template #graph-plug>
          <div class="c-my-panel">
            <div class="c-option-name">布局次数：{{graphOptions.layout.maxLayoutTimes}}</div>
            <el-slider v-model="graphOptions.layout.maxLayoutTimes" :min="10" :max="1000" :step="100" :show-tooltip="true"></el-slider>
            <div class="c-option-name">节点斥力系数：{{graphOptions.layout.force_node_repulsion}} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（设置太大会抖动）</div>
            <el-slider v-model="graphOptions.layout.force_node_repulsion" :min="0.01" :step="0.05" :max="4"></el-slider>
            <div class="c-option-name">连线牵引力系数：{{graphOptions.layout.force_line_elastic}} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（设置太大会抖动）</div>
            <el-slider v-model="graphOptions.layout.force_line_elastic" :min="0.01" :step="0.05" :max="4"></el-slider>
            <div class="c-option-name">观察对象：</div>
            <el-radio-group size="mini" v-model="configType">
              <el-radio-button label="node">Node</el-radio-button>
              <el-radio-button label="line">Line</el-radio-button>
            </el-radio-group>
            <div style="padding:5px;">
              <div v-if="configType === 'node'" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                <div class="c-option-name">随机范围：({{rangeForNode[0]}}, {{rangeForNode[1]}})</div>
                <el-slider v-model="rangeForNode" range :min="0.2" :max="30" />
                <el-link size="mini" plain type="primary" @click="randomNodeWeight">随机重置节点重量</el-link>
              </div>
              <div v-if="configType === 'line'" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                <div class="c-option-name">随机范围：({{rangeForLine[0]}}, {{rangeForLine[1]}})</div>
                <el-slider v-model="rangeForLine" range :min="0.2" :max="30" />
                <el-link size="mini" type="primary" @click="randomLineWeight">随机重置连线牵引力</el-link>
              </div>
            </div>
            <el-divider />
            <div style="padding:5px;">
              <el-button size="small" round type="primary" @click="updateLayouterOptions">应用并继续布局</el-button>
              <el-button size="small" round type="primary" @click="refresh">应用并刷新重新开始</el-button>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:10px;">
              <el-link size="mini" type="primary" @click="addNodes">给被选中的节点加两个子节点</el-link>
            </div>
          </div>
        </template>
      </RelationGraph>
    </div>
  </div>
</template>

<script>
// 如果您没有在main.js文件中使用Vue.use(RelationGraph); 就需要使用下面这一行代码来引入relation-graph
// import RelationGraph from 'relation-graph';
export default {
  name: 'Demo',
  components: { },
  data() {
    return {
      configType: 'node',
      rangeForNode: [0.1, 30],
      rangeForLine: [0.1, 4],
      graphOptions: {
        debug: false,
        defaultNodeBorderWidth: 0,
        allowSwitchLineShape: true,
        allowSwitchJunctionPoint: true,
        defaultLineShape: 1,
        'layout': {
          layoutName: 'force',
          maxLayoutTimes: 100,
          force_node_repulsion: 0.5,
          force_line_elastic: 0.5
        },
        defaultJunctionPoint: 'border'

        // 这里可以参考"Graph 图谱"中的参数进行设置
      }
    };
  },
  mounted() {
    this.showGraph();
  },
  beforeDestroy() {
    console.log('beforeDestroy stop layout');
    this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance().stopAutoLayout();
  },
  methods: {
    async showGraph() {
      const __graph_json_data = {
        "rootId": "root",
        "nodes": [{id: 'root', text: 'Root', force_weight: 600}],
        "lines": []
      };
      for (let index = 0;index<30;index++) {
        const newNode = {
          id: 'n' + index,
          text: ''
        };
        const newLine = {
          from: __graph_json_data.rootId,
          to: newNode.id,
          text: ''
        };
        __graph_json_data.nodes.push(newNode);
        __graph_json_data.lines.push(newLine);
      }
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      await graphInstance.setJsonData(__graph_json_data);
      this.randomNodeWeight();
    },
    onNodeClick(nodeObject, $event) {
      console.log('onNodeClick:', nodeObject);
    },
    onLineClick(lineObject, linkObject, $event) {
      console.log('onLineClick:', lineObject);
    },
    randomNodeWeight() {
      this.resetNodeAndLineForceOptions();
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      graphInstance.getNodes().forEach(node => {
        if (node === graphInstance.graphData.rootNode) return;
        const nodeWeight = this.rangeForNode[0] + Math.random() * this.rangeForNode[1];
        node.width = 10 + 10 * Math.sqrt(nodeWeight);
        node.height = 10 + 10 * Math.sqrt(nodeWeight);
        node.force_weight = nodeWeight;
        node.text = nodeWeight.toFixed(1);
      })
    },
    randomLineWeight() {
      this.resetNodeAndLineForceOptions();
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      graphInstance.getLinks().forEach(link => {
        const line = link.relations[0];
        const lineElastic = this.rangeForLine[0] + Math.random() * this.rangeForLine[1];
        line.force_elastic = lineElastic;
        line.text = lineElastic.toFixed(1);
      })
    },
    resetNodeAndLineForceOptions() {
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      graphInstance.getNodes().forEach(node => {
        if (node === graphInstance.graphData.rootNode) return;
        node.width = 30;
        node.height = 30;
        node.force_weight = undefined;
        node.text = '';
      });
      graphInstance.getLinks().forEach(link => {
        const line = link.relations[0];
        line.force_elastic = undefined;
        line.text = '';
      });
    },
    async updateLayouterOptions() {
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      await graphInstance.stopAutoLayout();
      graphInstance.layouter.maxLayoutTimes = this.graphOptions.layout.maxLayoutTimes;
      graphInstance.layouter.force_node_repulsion = this.graphOptions.layout.force_node_repulsion;
      graphInstance.layouter.force_line_elastic = this.graphOptions.layout.force_line_elastic;
      setTimeout(async() => {
        await graphInstance.startAutoLayout();
      }, 500);
    },
    async refresh() {
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      await graphInstance.stopAutoLayout();
      graphInstance.layouter.maxLayoutTimes = this.graphOptions.layout.maxLayoutTimes;
      graphInstance.layouter.force_node_repulsion = this.graphOptions.layout.force_node_repulsion;
      graphInstance.layouter.force_line_elastic = this.graphOptions.layout.force_line_elastic;
      graphInstance.refresh();
    },
    addNodes() {
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      const addToNodeId = graphInstance.options.checkedNodeId || graphInstance.graphData.rootNode.id;
      const newId = graphInstance.generateNewNodeId();
      const newNodes = [{
        id: newId + '-1',
        text: 'New node'
      }, {
        id: newId + '-2',
        text: 'New node'
      }];
      newNodes.forEach(n => { // 随机分配一个位置，避免重叠
        n.x = Math.floor(Math.random() * 40);
        n.y = Math.floor(Math.random() * 40);
      });
      graphInstance.addNodes(newNodes);
      graphInstance.addLines([{
        from: addToNodeId,
        to: newId + '-1',
        text: 'New'
      }, {
        from: addToNodeId,
        to: newId + '-2',
        text: 'New'
      }]);
      graphInstance.layouter.allNodes = graphInstance.graphData.nodes;
      graphInstance.layouter.allLinks = graphInstance.graphData.links;
      graphInstance.layouter.updateVisibleNodes();
      setTimeout(async() => {
        await graphInstance.startAutoLayout();
      }, 300);
    }
  }
};
</script>
<style lang="scss" scoped>
.c-my-panel{
  width: 400px;
  position: absolute;
  left: 10px;
  top: 10px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  z-index: 800;
  background-color: #efefef;
  border: #eeeeee solid 1px;
  padding: 10px;
  .c-option-name{
    color: #666666;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 30px;
  }
  .c-simple-configs {
    padding-left:70px;
    padding-right:70px;
    & > div {
      line-height: 30px;
      color: #5b05f1;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      &:hover{
        background-color: #5b05f1;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
    }
  }
}
</style>

Vue3 版本 ​

layout-force-options-pro.vue ​

javascript
<template>
  <div>
    <div style="height:calc(100vh);">
      <RelationGraph ref="graphRef" :options="graphOptions" :on-node-click="onNodeClick" :on-line-click="onLineClick">
        <template #graph-plug>
          <div class="c-my-panel">
            <div class="c-option-name">Layout Times: {{ graphOptions.layout.maxLayoutTimes }}</div>
            <el-slider v-model="graphOptions.layout.maxLayoutTimes" :min="10" :max="1000" :step="100" :show-tooltip="true" />
            <div class="c-option-name">Node Repulsion Coefficient: {{ graphOptions.layout.force_node_repulsion }} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（Setting it too large will cause shaking）</div>
            <el-slider v-model="graphOptions.layout.force_node_repulsion" :min="0.01" :step="0.05" :max="4" />
            <div class="c-option-name">Line Elastic Coefficient: {{ graphOptions.layout.force_line_elastic }} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（Setting it too large will cause shaking）</div>
            <el-slider v-model="graphOptions.layout.force_line_elastic" :min="0.01" :step="0.05" :max="4" />
            <div class="c-option-name">Observation Object:</div>
            <el-radio-group v-model="configType" size="small">
              <el-radio-button label="node">Node</el-radio-button>
              <el-radio-button label="line">Line</el-radio-button>
            </el-radio-group>
            <div style="padding:5px;">
              <div v-if="configType === 'node'" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                <div class="c-option-name">Random Range: ({{ rangeForNode[0] }}, {{ rangeForNode[1] }})</div>
                <el-slider v-model="rangeForNode" range :min="0.2" :max="30" />
                <el-link size="small" plain type="primary" @click="randomNodeWeight">Randomly Reset Node Weight</el-link>
              </div>
              <div v-if="configType === 'line'" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                <div class="c-option-name">Random Range: ({{ rangeForLine[0] }}, {{ rangeForLine[1] }})</div>
                <el-slider v-model="rangeForLine" range :min="0.2" :max="30" />
                <el-link size="small" type="primary" @click="randomLineWeight">Randomly Reset Line Elastic</el-link>
              </div>
            </div>
            <el-divider />
            <div style="padding:5px;">
              <el-button size="small" round type="primary" @click="updateLayouterOptions">Apply and Continue Layout</el-button>
              <el-button size="small" round type="primary" @click="refresh">Apply and Refresh</el-button>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:10px;">
              <el-link size="small" type="primary" @click="addNodes">Add Two Child Nodes to Selected Nodes</el-link>
            </div>
          </div>
        </template>
      </RelationGraph>
    </div>
  </div>
</template>

<script lang="ts" setup>
import RelationGraph from 'relation-graph-vue3';
import type { RGOptions, RGNode, RGLine, RGLink, RGUserEvent, RGJsonData, RelationGraphComponent } from 'relation-graph-vue3';
import {onBeforeUnmount, onMounted, onUnmounted, ref} from 'vue';

const graphRef = ref<RelationGraphComponent>();
const configType = ref('node');
const rangeForNode = ref([0.1, 30]);
const rangeForLine = ref([0.1, 4]);
const graphOptions = ref<RGOptions>( {
    debug: false,
    defaultNodeBorderWidth: 0,
    allowSwitchLineShape: true,
    allowSwitchJunctionPoint: true,
    defaultLineShape: 1,
    layout: {
        layoutName: 'force',
        maxLayoutTimes: 100,
        force_node_repulsion: 0.5,
        force_line_elastic: 0.5

    },
    defaultJunctionPoint: 'border'
});

onMounted(() => {
    showGraph();
});
onBeforeUnmount(() => {
    graphRef.value!.getInstance().stopAutoLayout();
});
const  showGraph = async() => {
    const __graph_json_data: RGJsonData = {
        rootId: 'root',
        nodes: [{ id: 'root', text: 'Root', force_weight: 600 }],
        lines: []
    };
    for (let index = 0; index < 30; index++) {
        const newNode: RGNode = {
            id: 'n' + index,
            text: ''
        };
        const newLine: RGLine = {
            from: __graph_json_data.rootId,
            to: newNode.id,
            text: ''
        };
        __graph_json_data.nodes.push(newNode);
        __graph_json_data.lines.push(newLine);
    }
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    await graphInstance.setJsonData(__graph_json_data);
    randomNodeWeight();
};
const onNodeClick = (nodeObject: RGNode, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onNodeClick:', nodeObject);
};
const onLineClick = (lineObject: RGLine, linkObject: RGLink, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onLineClick:', lineObject);
};
const randomNodeWeight = () => {
    resetNodeAndLineForceOptions();
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.getNodes().forEach(node => {
        if (node === graphInstance.graphData.rootNode) return;
        const nodeWeight = rangeForNode.value[0] + Math.random() * rangeForNode.value[1];
        node.width = 10 + 10 * Math.sqrt(nodeWeight);
        node.height = 10 + 10 * Math.sqrt(nodeWeight);
        node.force_weight = nodeWeight;
        node.text = nodeWeight.toFixed(1);
    });
};
const randomLineWeight = () => {
    resetNodeAndLineForceOptions();
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.getLinks().forEach(link => {
        const line = link.relations[0];
        const lineElastic = rangeForLine.value[0] + Math.random() * rangeForLine.value[1];
        line.force_elastic = lineElastic;
        line.text = lineElastic.toFixed(1);
    });
};
const resetNodeAndLineForceOptions = () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.getNodes().forEach(node => {
        if (node === graphInstance.graphData.rootNode) return;
        node.width = 30;
        node.height = 30;
        node.force_weight = undefined;
        node.text = '';
    });
    graphInstance.getLinks().forEach(link => {
        const line = link.relations[0];
        line.force_elastic = undefined;
        line.text = '';
    });
};
const  updateLayouterOptions = async() => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    await graphInstance.stopAutoLayout();
    graphInstance.layouter.maxLayoutTimes = graphOptions.value.layout.maxLayoutTimes;
    graphInstance.layouter.force_node_repulsion = graphOptions.value.layout.force_node_repulsion;
    graphInstance.layouter.force_line_elastic = graphOptions.value.layout.force_line_elastic;
    setTimeout(async () => {
        await graphInstance.startAutoLayout();
    }, 500);
};
const  refresh = async() => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    await graphInstance.stopAutoLayout();
    graphInstance.layouter.maxLayoutTimes = graphOptions.value.layout.maxLayoutTimes;
    graphInstance.layouter.force_node_repulsion = graphOptions.value.layout.force_node_repulsion;
    graphInstance.layouter.force_line_elastic = graphOptions.value.layout.force_line_elastic;
    graphInstance.refresh();
};
const addNodes = () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    const addToNodeId = graphInstance.options.checkedNodeId || graphInstance.graphData.rootNode.id;
    const newId = graphInstance.generateNewNodeId();
    const newNodes: RGNode[] = [
        {
            id: newId + '-1',
            text: 'New node'
        },
        {
            id: newId + '-2',
            text: 'New node'
        }
    ];
    newNodes.forEach(n => {
        n.x = Math.floor(Math.random() * 40);
        n.y = Math.floor(Math.random() * 40);
    });
    graphInstance.addNodes(newNodes);
    graphInstance.addLines([
        {
            from: addToNodeId,
            to: newId + '-1',
            text: 'New'
        },
        {
            from: addToNodeId,
            to: newId + '-2',
            text: 'New'
        }
    ]);
    graphInstance.layouter.allNodes = graphInstance.graphData.nodes;
    graphInstance.layouter.allLinks = graphInstance.graphData.links;
    graphInstance.layouter.updateVisibleNodes();
    setTimeout(async () => {
        await graphInstance.startAutoLayout();
    }, 300);
};
</script>

React 版本 ​

layout-force-options-pro.tsx ​

javascript
import React, {useEffect, useRef, useState} from 'react';
import RelationGraph, {
  JsonLine,
  JsonNode,
  Layout,
  RGForceLayoutOptions,
  RGLayouter,
  RGTreeLayoutOptions
} from 'relation-graph-react';
import type { RGOptions, RGNode, RGLine, RGLink, RGUserEvent, RGJsonData, RelationGraphComponent } from 'relation-graph-react';
import { CircumIcon } from './RGDemoComponents/MyDemoIcons';
import './layout-force-options-pro.scss';
import {MyButton, MyLinkButton, MyRangeSlider, MySelector, MySlider} from "./RGDemoComponents/MyUIComponents";

const MyMainComponent: React.FC = () => {
  const graphRef = useRef<RelationGraphComponent|null>(null);
  const [configType, setConfigType] = useState('node');
  const [maxLayoutTimes, setMaxLayoutTimes] = useState(3000);
  const [force_node_repulsion, setForce_node_repulsion] = useState(1);
  const [force_line_elastic, setForce_line_elastic] = useState(1);
  const [rangeForNode, setRangeForNode] = useState([0.1, 30]);
  const [rangeForLine, setRangeForLine] = useState([0.1, 4]);
  const changeOptionsTimer = useRef<number>(0);
  const graphOptions: RGOptions = {
    debug: false,
    defaultNodeBorderWidth: 0,
    allowSwitchLineShape: true,
    allowSwitchJunctionPoint: true,
    defaultLineShape: 1,
    layout: {
      layoutName: 'force',
      maxLayoutTimes: 3000,
      force_node_repulsion: 0.5,
      force_line_elastic: 0.5

    },
    defaultJunctionPoint: 'border'
  };

  const showGraph = async () => {
    const __graph_json_data: RGJsonData = {
      rootId: 'root',
      nodes: [{ id: 'root', text: 'Root', force_weight: 600 }],
      lines: []
    };
    for (let index = 0; index < 30; index++) {
      const newNode: JsonNode = {
        id: 'n' + index,
        text: ''
      };
      const newLine: JsonLine = {
        from: __graph_json_data.rootId!,
        to: newNode.id,
        text: ''
      };
      __graph_json_data.nodes.push(newNode);
      __graph_json_data.lines.push(newLine);
    }
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current?.getInstance();
    await graphInstance?.setJsonData(__graph_json_data);
    randomNodeWeight();
  };

  const onNodeClick = (nodeObject: RGNode, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onNodeClick:', nodeObject);
  };

  const onLineClick = (lineObject: RGLine, linkObject: RGLink, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onLineClick:', lineObject);
  };

  const randomNodeWeight = async () => {
    resetNodeAndLineForceOptions();
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.getNodes().forEach(node => {
      if (node === graphInstance.graphData.rootNode) return;
      const nodeWeight = rangeForNode[0] + Math.random() * rangeForNode[1];
      node.width = 10 + 10 * Math.sqrt(nodeWeight);
      node.height = 10 + 10 * Math.sqrt(nodeWeight);
      node.force_weight = nodeWeight;
      node.text = nodeWeight.toFixed(1);
    });
    graphInstance.dataUpdated();
    await graphInstance.startAutoLayout();
  };

  const randomLineWeight = async () => {
    resetNodeAndLineForceOptions();
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.getLinks().forEach(link => {
      const line = link.relations[0];
      const lineElastic = rangeForLine[0] + Math.random() * rangeForLine[1];
      line.force_elastic = lineElastic;
      line.text = lineElastic.toFixed(1);
    });
    await graphInstance.dataUpdated();
    await graphInstance.startAutoLayout();
  };

  const resetNodeAndLineForceOptions = () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.getNodes().forEach(node => {
      if (node === graphInstance.graphData.rootNode) return;
      node.width = 30;
      node.height = 30;
      node.force_weight = undefined;
      node.text = '';
    });
    graphInstance?.getLinks().forEach(link => {
      const line = link.relations[0];
      line.force_elastic = undefined;
      line.text = '';
    });
  };

  const realUpdateLayouterOptions = async () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    await graphInstance.stopAutoLayout();
    const layoutOptions = graphInstance.layouter.layoutOptions as RGForceLayoutOptions;
    layoutOptions.maxLayoutTimes = maxLayoutTimes;
    layoutOptions.force_node_repulsion = force_node_repulsion;
    layoutOptions.force_line_elastic = force_line_elastic;
    // For compatibility, you need to set it up again
    graphInstance.layouter.maxLayoutTimes = maxLayoutTimes;
    graphInstance.layouter.force_node_repulsion = force_node_repulsion;
    graphInstance.layouter.force_line_elastic = force_line_elastic;
    setTimeout(async () => {
      await graphInstance?.startAutoLayout();
    }, 500);
  };
  const updateLayouterOptions = async () => {
    if (changeOptionsTimer.current) {
      clearTimeout(changeOptionsTimer.current);
    }
    changeOptionsTimer.current = setTimeout(() => {
      realUpdateLayouterOptions();
    }, 500);
  };
  const refresh = async () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    await graphInstance?.stopAutoLayout();
    const layoutOptions = graphInstance.layouter.layoutOptions as RGForceLayoutOptions;
    layoutOptions.maxLayoutTimes = maxLayoutTimes;
    layoutOptions.force_node_repulsion = force_node_repulsion;
    layoutOptions.force_line_elastic = force_line_elastic;
    await graphInstance.refresh();
  };

  const addNodes = () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    const addToNodeId = graphInstance.options.checkedNodeId || graphInstance.graphData.rootNode!.id;
    const newId = graphInstance.generateNewNodeId();
    const newNodes: JsonNode[] = [
      {
        id: newId + '-1',
        text: 'New node'
      },
      {
        id: newId + '-2',
        text: 'New node'
      }
    ];
    newNodes.forEach(n => {
      n.x = Math.floor(Math.random() * 40);
      n.y = Math.floor(Math.random() * 40);
    });
    graphInstance.addNodes(newNodes);
    graphInstance.addLines([
      {
        from: addToNodeId,
        to: newId + '-1',
        text: 'New'
      },
      {
        from: addToNodeId,
        to: newId + '-2',
        text: 'New'
      }
    ]);
    graphInstance.layouter.allNodes = graphInstance.graphData.nodes;
    graphInstance.layouter.allLinks = graphInstance.graphData.links;
    graphInstance.layouter.updateVisibleNodes();
    setTimeout(async () => {
      await graphInstance?.startAutoLayout();
    }, 300);
  };

  useEffect(() => {
    showGraph();
    return () => {
      graphRef.current?.getInstance().stopAutoLayout();
    };
  }, []);
  useEffect(() => {
    updateLayouterOptions();
  }, [maxLayoutTimes, force_node_repulsion, force_line_elastic])
  return (
    <div>
      <div style={{ height: '100vh' }}>
        <div className="c-my-panel rounded-lg absolute left-20 top-20 z-20 p-4 bg-white border-solid border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
          <div style={{width: '500px'}}>
            <div className="c-option-name">Layout Times: {maxLayoutTimes}</div>
            <MySlider currentValue={maxLayoutTimes} min={10} max={1000} step={100} onChange={(newValue) => {setMaxLayoutTimes(newValue)}} />
            <div className="c-option-name">Node Repulsion Coefficient: {force_node_repulsion} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（Setting it too large will cause shaking）</div>
            <MySlider currentValue={force_node_repulsion} min={0.01} step={0.05} max={4} onChange={(newValue) => {setForce_node_repulsion(newValue)}} />
            <div className="c-option-name">Line Elastic Coefficient: {force_line_elastic} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（Setting it too large will cause shaking）</div>
            <MySlider currentValue={force_line_elastic} min={0.01} step={0.05} max={4} onChange={(newValue) => {setForce_line_elastic(newValue)}} />
          </div>
          <div className="border border-gray-500 rounded-lg p-2">
            <div className="c-option-name">Observation Object:</div>
            <div className="w-36">
              <MySelector
                data={[
                  { value: 'node', text: 'Node' },
                  { value: 'line', text: 'Line' }
                ]}
                currentValue={configType}
                onChange={(newValue: string, label) => { setConfigType(newValue); }}
              />
            </div>
            <div style={{ padding: '5px' }}>
              <div style={{ display: configType === 'node' ? 'block' : 'none', paddingRight: '10px' }}>
                <div className="c-option-name">Random Range: ({rangeForNode[0]}, {rangeForNode[1]})</div>
                <MyRangeSlider currentValue={rangeForNode} min={0.2} max={30} onChange={(newValue) => {setRangeForNode(newValue)}} />
                <MyLinkButton onClick={()=>{randomNodeWeight();}}>Randomly Reset Node Weight</MyLinkButton>
              </div>
              <div style={{ display: configType === 'line' ? 'block' : 'none', paddingRight: '10px' }}>
                <div className="c-option-name">Random Range: ({rangeForLine[0]}, {rangeForLine[1]})</div>
                <MyRangeSlider currentValue={rangeForLine} min={0.2} max={30} onChange={(newValue) => {setRangeForLine(newValue)}} />
                <MyLinkButton onClick={()=>{randomLineWeight();}}>Randomly Reset Line Elastic</MyLinkButton>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr />
          {/*<div style={{ padding: '5px' }}>*/}
          {/*  <MyButton onClick={() => {updateLayouterOptions();}}>Apply and Continue Layout</MyButton>*/}
          {/*  <MyButton onClick={() => {refresh();}}>Apply and Refresh</MyButton>*/}
          {/*</div>*/}
          <div style={{ padding: '10px' }}>
            <MyLinkButton onClick={() => {addNodes();}}>Add Two Child Nodes to Selected Nodes</MyLinkButton>
          </div>
        </div>
        <RelationGraph ref={graphRef} options={graphOptions} onNodeClick={onNodeClick} onLineClick={onLineClick}>
        </RelationGraph>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default MyMainComponent;

const MyDemoIcons: React.FC<{
  name: string,
  size: string,
  color: string,
}> = ({ name, size, color }) => {
  const displayIcon = icons.find((e) => e.name === name)
  const _size = size || '32px'
  const _color = color || 'currentColor'
  return (
    <svg
      className={'circumicon__' + name}
      width={_size}
      height={_color}
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill={color}
      dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: displayIcon.svg }}
    ></svg>
  )
}
export default MyDemoIcons

import React from "react";

export interface MySelectorProps {
  small?: boolean
  currentValue: string|number
  data:{value: string|number, text:string}[]
  onChange: (newValue:string|number, label:string) => void
}
export const MySelector:React.FC<MySelectorProps> = ({small, data, onChange, currentValue}) => {
  return (
    <div className="flex flex-wrap justify-center rounded-lg border border-gray-900 overflow-hidden">
      {
        data.map(item =>
          <div key={item.value}
               className={`border-r w-auto text-xs cursor-pointer whitespace-nowrap ${currentValue === item.value && 'bg-blue-500 text-white'} ${small?' px-2 h-6 leading-6':'h-8 px-3 leading-8'}`}
               onClick={() => {onChange(item.value, item.text);}}
          >
          {item.text}
        </div>)
      }
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MySwitchProps {
  currentValue: boolean
  onChange: (newValue:boolean) => void
}
export const MySwitch:React.FC<MySwitchProps> = ({onChange, currentValue}) => {
  return (
    <div className={`w-14 flex rounded-full border p-0.5 ${currentValue ? 'justify-end border-blue-500' : 'justify-start border-gray-500'}`}>
      <div
        className={`w-8 h-5 leading-8 rounded-full w-auto px-3 text-xs cursor-pointer whitespace-nowrap ${currentValue ? 'bg-blue-500' : 'bg-gray-500'}`} onClick={() => {onChange(!currentValue);}}>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MySliderProps {
  min: number
  max: number
  step: number
  currentValue: number
  onChange: (newValue:number) => void
}
export const MySlider:React.FC<MySliderProps> = ({min, max, step, currentValue, onChange}) => {
  return (
    <div>
      <input
        type="range"
        className="w-72"
        min={min}
        max={max}
        step={step}
        value={currentValue}
        onChange={(e) => { onChange(parseFloat(e.target.value))}}
      />
    </div>
  );
};

export interface MyRangeSliderProps {
  min: number
  max: number
  step: number
  currentValue: [number, number]
  onChange: (newValue:[number, number]) => void
}
export const MyRangeSlider:React.FC<MyRangeSliderProps> = ({min, max, step, currentValue, onChange}) => {
  return (
    <div className="w-72">
      <div>Min:</div>
      <input
        type="range"
        className="w-full"
        min={min}
        max={max}
        step={step}
        value={currentValue[0]}
        onChange={(e) => { if (parseFloat(e.target.value) < currentValue[1]) onChange([parseFloat(e.target.value), currentValue[1]])}}
      />
      <div>Max:</div>
      <input
        type="range"
        className="w-full"
        min={min}
        max={max}
        step={step}
        value={currentValue[1]}
        onChange={(e) => { if (parseFloat(e.target.value) > currentValue[0]) onChange([currentValue[0], parseFloat(e.target.value)])}}
      />
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MyButtonProps {
  onClick: () => void
  disabled?: boolean
}
export const MyButton:React.FC<MyButtonProps> = ({children, onClick, disabled}) => {
  return (
    <button className={`mr-2 px-2 py-1 rounded ${disabled===true ? 'bg-gray-300 text-black cursor-not-allowed':'bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white'}`}
            onClick={()=>{onClick();}}>{children}</button>
  );
};
export interface MyLinkButtonProps {
  onClick: () => void
}
export const MyLinkButton:React.FC<MyLinkButtonProps> = ({children, onClick}) => {
  return (
    <div className="text-blue-600 cursor-pointer underline decoration-1" onClick={()=>{onClick();}}>
      {children}
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MyCheckBoxProps {
  currentValue: string|number
  data:{value: string|number, text:string}[]
  onChange: (newValue:string|number, label:string) => void
}
export const MyCheckBox:React.FC<MyCheckBoxProps> = ({data, onChange, currentValue}) => {
  // console.log(data);
  return (
    <div className="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
      {
        data.map(thisItem =>
          <div
            key={thisItem.value}
            className={`px-1 py-0.5 flex justify-center place-items-center rounded-sm text-sm cursor-pointer  hover:bg-gray-300 ${currentValue === thisItem.value ? 'text-blue-600':'text-gray-500'}`}
            onClick={()=>{onChange(thisItem.value, thisItem.text);}}
          >
            <div className={`w-4 h-4 mr-1 rounded-full ${currentValue === thisItem.value ? 'border border-blue-500 bg-blue-500 text-blue-600':'border border-gray-500 text-gray-500'}`}></div>
            {thisItem.text}
          </div>
        )
      }
    </div>
  );
};
export interface CheckboxOption {
  value: string | number;
  text: string;
}

export interface MyMultiCheckBoxProps {
  currentValue: (string | number)[];
  checkboxOptions: CheckboxOption[];
  onChange: (newValue: (string | number)[]) => void;
}
export const MyMultiCheckBox:React.FC<MyMultiCheckBoxProps> = ({data, onChange, currentValue}) => {
  // console.log(data);
  const onClickItem = (item: string | number) => {
    const newValue = currentValue.includes(item)
      ? currentValue.filter((value) => value !== item)
      : [...currentValue, item];
    onChange(newValue);
  };
  return (
    <div className="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
      {
        data.map(thisItem =>
          <div
            key={thisItem.value}
            className={`px-1 py-0.5 flex justify-center place-items-center rounded-sm text-sm cursor-pointer  hover:bg-gray-300 ${currentValue === thisItem.value ? 'text-blue-600':'text-gray-500'}`}
            onClick={()=>{onClickItem(thisItem.value);}}
          >
            <div className={`w-4 h-4 mr-1 rounded-full ${currentValue.includes(thisItem.value) ? 'border border-blue-500 bg-blue-500 text-blue-600':'border border-gray-500 text-gray-500'}`}></div>
            {thisItem.text}
          </div>
        )
      }
    </div>
  );
};

  console.warn(messageObject);
}
export const ElNotification = (messageObject) => {
  console.warn(messageObject);
